{
  "texts": [
    "This guide will provide stepby-step instructions on how to create an account, so that you can start connecting with your colleagues 1.",
    "Download the app from your device's app store 2.",
    "Open the app and select \"Create Account\" from the home screen 3.",
    "Enter your name, email address, and a password of your choice in the provided fields (make sure it is something you will remember) 4.",
    "Select \"Create Account\" at the bottom of the page when finished entering information in all fields 5."
  ]
}